node.text:
Good days and bad days… we all have them. But no matter how you slice it, even the bad days have a little sweetness in them. 💕 Take, for instance, last evening I had a virtual interview scheduled and there was no WiFi or cell service. 😲That situation was frustrating because it was out of my control, but I packed up my things and went to a local boutique hotel to get connected, while enjoying my cigar. I love my job because the good always outweighs the bad. What sweet silver lining have you found on a bad day recently? ✊
.
.
.
.
.
